	* Merged gmp-1.99.3+ mpn code from tege for printf_fp.
	* stdio/printf_fp.c: Include "longlong.h"; gmp-impl.h no longer does.
	
	* Makerules (+depfiles): Filter $(extra-objs) to get only .o files.

