	* sysdeps/stub/dbl2mpn.c, sysdeps/iee754/dbl2mpn.c: New files.
	* sysdeps/stub/asm.h: New file.
	* sysdeps/m68k/add_n.S, sysdeps/m68k/addmul_1.S,
