	* sysdeps/unix/bsd/alarm.c: There are 1000000 usecs in a sec.

	* sysdeps/unix/bsd/sun/ptrace.c: Removed.

	* stdio/fgets.c: For unbuffered stream, don't return EOF after
	reading some data.
	Added missing parens.

